🤳 follow @jooliesdates
🩷 like this post

Giveaway is open to US residents, who are 18+ years of age. No purchase necessary to enter or win giveaway. Giveaway starts 3/17/25 at 10AM PST and ends 3/20/25 at 11:59PM PST.
